<i>noun</i>: 편협성 [편협썽], 편협 [편협] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>편협성 [편협썽]</dt><br>
<dd>narrow-minded bigotry; intolerance</dd><br>
<dd>한쪽으로 치우쳐 생각이나 마음이 좁고 너그럽지 못한 성질이나 특성.</dd><br>
<dd>One's personality or characteristic being petty and not generous, as it is biased.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>편협 [편협]</dt><br>
<dd>being narrow-minded; intolerance</dd><br>
<dd>한쪽으로 치우쳐 생각이나 마음이 좁고 너그럽지 못함.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of one's thought or mind being petty and not generous, as it is biased.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>